d0\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-38e8328\" data-id=\"38e8328\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0b033d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e0b033d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">What Are Some Effective Control Methods For Smoky Brown Cockroaches?\u200b<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2254c0e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2254c0e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>One of the most effective control methods for Smoky Brown Cockroaches is to maintain a clean and dry environment. These roaches thrive in areas with moisture, so it&#8217;s important to fix any leaky pipes or faucets and remove all standing water. Cleaning up food crumbs and spills immediately can discourage these pests from residing in your home.<\/p><p>Another control method for Smoky Brown Cockroaches is to seal off any potential entry points into your home. This includes repairing or replacing damaged weather stripping around doors and windows, sealing gaps around pipes and vents, and filling in cracks or holes in walls. Limiting their access points can reduce the chances of these roaches finding their way inside.<\/p><p>Finally, using insecticides specifically designed for cockroach control can effectively eliminate Smoky Brown Cockroaches. However, following instructions carefully and using caution when applying these products is important, as they can be harmful if not used properly. Consulting with ACME Pest Solutions may also help determine the best action to control these pests.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d90eca9 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d90eca9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-07b4658\" data-id=\"07b4658\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5c9651 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"f5c9651\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"Article\",\r\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\r\n    \"@id\": \"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/smoky-brown-cockroaches\/\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"headline\": \"Smoky Brown Cockroaches\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Smoky Brown cockroaches are that they have wings that extend beyond their bodies by about an inch. This helps them to fly short distances, although they typically prefer to scuttle along on the ground or climb up walls and other vertical surfaces.\",\r\n  \"image\": \"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Smoky-Brown-Cockroaches-1.jpg\",  \r\n  \"author\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Person\",\r\n    \"name\": \"adminmaster\",\r\n    \"url\": \"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/\"\r\n  },  \r\n  \"publisher\": {\r\n    \"@t